  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study the effects of mineralocorticoid stimulation on social cognition will be
      investigated in healthy young individuals.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      80 healthy young individuals (40 females and 40 male) will be recruited an randomized to
      either placebo or 0.4 mg Fludrocortison before testing. Tasks will on emotion recognition,
      Task Switch, visual spacial memory and decision making will be conducted.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
